<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Claim Rejected</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333;">
    <h2>Your Claim Has Been Rejected</h2>
    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    <p>
      Unfortunately, your claim has been <strong>rejected</strong>.
    </p>

    <table cellpadding="6" cellspacing="0" border="1" style="border-collapse: collapse;">
      {{!-- <tr> --}}
        {{!-- <td><strong>Claim ID</strong></td> --}}
        {{!-- <td>{{claimId}}</td> --}}
      {{!-- </tr> --}}
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Type</strong></td>
        <td>{{claimType}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Amount</strong></td>
        <td>{{amount}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Date of Expense</strong></td>
        <td>{{dateOfExpense}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Notes</strong></td>
        <td>{{notes}}</td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <p>If you believe this was a mistake, please contact your manager for clarification.</p>
    <p>Best regards,<br />EMS</p>
  </body>
</html>
